"im not even mad that u said it. no wait. i am. more so the fact that i said in my post u appreciate people for who they are and dont want them to change. and clearly this isnt true. u completely proved that wrong just now. how could u write it then have me read it then deny that it was about me. u want to know how i feel well thats it. i turned on my computer just for this."
